<DocsPageTitle Path="Extensions/SVG Chart Animation">
    Blazorise SVG Chart Animation
</DocsPageTitle>

<DocsPageLead>
    Animate SVG chart loading and data updates with C# and Blazor options.
</DocsPageLead>

<DocsPageParagraph>
    SVG chart animation can be declared with <Code>SvgChartAnimation</Code> or configured with <Code>SvgChartOptions.Animation</Code>. Animation targets are grouped by SVG behavior, such as geometry and opacity, and each target can override timing, easing, and load/update behavior. Streaming animations remain configured separately with <Code>SvgChartStreamingOptions.Animation</Code>.
</DocsPageParagraph>

<DocsPageSubtitle>
    Examples
</DocsPageSubtitle>

<DocsPageSection>
    <DocsPageSectionHeader Title="Declarative animation">
        Add <Code>SvgChartAnimation</Code> inside a chart to animate the first render and subsequent updates.
    </DocsPageSectionHeader>
